# Hound is a code search tool. The following is instruction on how to run it on local server.

1. Download Docker <br />
2. Download config.json from this repository <br />
3. Run the following commands: <br />
docker run -d -p 6080:6080 --name hound -v $(pwd):/data etsy/hound <br />
docker run etsy/hound <br />
